title: Outwitting the Law: The Film That Uncovers Small Town Hate - Girl on a Chain Gang 1966

sources.title: Outwitting the Law: The Film That Uncovers Small Town Hate - Girl on a Chain Gang 1966
sources.description:
Three people are framed, arrested, and thrown into prison by corrupt Southern police, who put them to work on a chain gang.


Original title: Girl on a Chain Gang (1966)
Directed & Written by Jerry Gross

Main cast:
Julie Ange - Diane
William Watson - Bill
Ron Charles - Paul
Arlene Farber - Nellie
Ron Segal - Ted Branch
Peter Nevard - Deputy Cal

Genres: Colorized, Crime, Drama
Release date: October 21, 1966 
Filming location: New York, USA

Black & White version: https://youtu.be/y9h3paKn7iM
